{"tid":2170414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少女跳樓自殺身亡　親父欲接住遭壓死","createTime":"2020-08-23T08:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T10:28:31.000Z","uid":50386,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"695609fd15e4b937e18d7d180944b119b37fcb9b","tid":2170414,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"四川瀘州市瀘縣一名15歲曾姓少女周六（22日）上午突然從25層高的頂樓上跳下，她的42歲父親站在樓下，試圖接住女兒，詎料被砸傷。兩人隨後送院搶救，惟搶救無效死亡。警方同日通報稱，正調查事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n警方在通報稱，瀘縣藍山郡小區內發生一宗墮樓事件，曾女跳樓後，砸中樓下試圖接住她的父親。有現場目擊者表示，多名民眾驚叫一聲，「他想接住，但女孩直接把他砸中了」。<br />\n<br />\n網傳影片顯示，曾女站在頂樓邊緣，躍下後急速墮落地面，其身穿白色上衣的父親在樓下試圖接住女兒無果。曾父情緒激動，不斷呼叫女兒的名字，惟兩人送院不治身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cmy5d8M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmy5d8M.png&h=4387990b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUASDAs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUASDAs.png&h=d032652c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90f4465f3f3255fb547b9ea57fb47350c13b3bb1","tid":2170414,"uid":208376,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:59:16.000Z","msg":"good 一齊離開鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f32c3c149d17fba5b41349aa767a21fdb38655","tid":2170414,"uid":108201,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"好事黎，一齊唔洗再做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d8dd3df8f2cba0838fd7c51e74d15f402279b5","tid":2170414,"uid":282352,"like":2,"dislike":52,"score":-50,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"黑警殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92009bb940779ce31c3bb5269a5097a408d22399","tid":2170414,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:01:51.000Z","msg":"好慘"},{"pid":"a7d2f5a523a6812697bed9f27de3597f545a968e","tid":2170414,"uid":219398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"73d8dd